<bibRefCitation id="1CC2F542FD510CCAA41D1E9408A424F4" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1093/aesa/61.1.228" author="Clarke, JFG" journalOrPublisher="Annals of the Entomological Society of America" pageId="0" pageNumber="169" pagination="228 - 229" refId="B10" refString="Clarke, JFG, 1967. The correct name for the Mimosa Webworm (Lepidoptera: Glyphipterigidae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America 61 (1): 228 - 229, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1093/aesa/61.1.228" title="The correct name for the Mimosa Webworm (Lepidoptera: Glyphipterigidae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1093/aesa/61.1.228" volume="61" year="1967">Clarke (1967</bibRefCitation>
